  "doc_id": "43106",
  "text": "This study examined 2 different intravitreal bevacizumab injection dosing schedules in patients with ME secondary to BRVO. Previous reports have shown successful outcomes with bevacizumab treatment in patients with RVO following either an as-needed dosing schedule [CITATION_1] or 3 monthly injections followed by as-needed dosing [CITATION_2] . Herein, we compare these 2 treatment schedules in a single-center retrospective study.",
